* (GPRS/EDGE/UMTS/HSDPA), creating an ad-hoc Wifi Access HotSpot. *
*******************************************************************
*                  OPEN GARDEN FOUNDATION                         *
*                   http://opengarden.net                         *
*                   "You are the network!"                        *
*                "Bandwidth Sharing is Nice!"                     *
